                    <h2 class="text-center mt-0">VEDO / I SEE MANZONI</h2>
                    <hr class="divider" />
                    <p>Vedo Manzoni presents, through a <a href="https://dlrc.ficlit.unibo.it/s/lib/faceted-browse/7">dedicated section</a> of <a href="https://dl.ficlit.unibo.it/s/lib/page/home">of the Digital Library</a> 
                        of <a href="https://ficlit.unibo.it/it">the Department of Classical Philology and Italian Studies at the University of Bologna</a>, 
                        the complete reproduction of the Quarantana and the metadata of the iconographic apparatus. This allows users to select the 505 vignettes throughout the various thematic paths.</p>
